The given triples will be associated with the topic: Politician. Ensure that the generated text is fluent, grammatically correct, and maintains the meaning of the original data. There can be multiple triples given that make up a complex sentence. (Antwerp | cityServed | Antwerp International Airport)

(City of Brussels | capital | Belgium)

"Antwerp International Airport serves the city of Antwerp which is in Belgium, where the capital is Brussels."
